chaaraNa|चारण
Cāraṇa  (EI 3), same as Vidyā-cāraṇa, a Jain monk endowed with magical powers. Cf. harita-pakva-sasy-ekṣu-cāraṇa-lavaṇ-opamardana (IE 8-5);<BR>grazing of cattle.

