kLLipta|कॢप्त
kḷpta  (CII 3, 4;<BR>HRS), cf. sa-kḷpt-opakḷpta (IE 8-5);<BR>probably, the tax on permanent tenants or the fixed revenue;<BR>fixed tax which is one of the seven sources of revenue specified in the Arthaśāstra; cf. upakḷpta, kḷpta-kara, udraṅga, kḷpta-śluka, etc.

kLLiptakara|कॢप्तकर
