nandaavilakku|नन्दाविलक्कु
nandā-vil8akku  (SII 1, 2), also spelt as nondā^0, nundā^0; a perpetual lamp;<BR>same as nandā-dīpa, akhaṇḍa-dīpa.

nandiimukha|नन्दीमुख
nandīmukha  (CII 1), a species of water-birds.

