rathaaShTamii|रथाष्टमी
rath-āṣṭamī  EI 29;<BR>CII 4;<BR>IA 17), same as Māgha śu-di 8.

rathayaatraa|रथयात्रा
ratha-yātrā  (EI 11), a festival.

rathika|रथिक
Rathika,  superintendent of chariots (Ep. Ind., Vol. XVIII, p. 156).

