raayarekha|रायरेख
rāya-rekha  (IA 15), a system of land measurement.

raayasa|रायस
Rāyasa  (EI 3, 17;<BR>ASLV), Kannaḍa;<BR>a secretary;<BR>an officer in the Vijayanagara administration.

raayasa|रायस
rāyasa  (ASLV), royal order. (SITI), office of a writer;<BR>clerkship;<BR>order of the king;<BR>written orders. Cf. Rāyasa-svāmin, head of the rāyasa.

raayasasvaamin|रायसस्वामिन्
Rāyasa-svāmin  (ASLV), ‘the head of the rāyasa’ (SITI);<BR>the chief secretary.

Rddhi|ऋद्धि
ṛddhi  (EI 3), supernatural power.

Rddhipaada|ऋद्धिपाद
ṛddhi-pāda,  cf. iddhi-pāda (EI 5), Buddhist;<BR>four in number.

reDDi|रेड्डि
Reḍḍi  (ASLV), a village official.

rekhaa|रेखा
rekhā  (EI 19), a land measure. Cf. rekai, rekai-ppon (SITI), irekai; regarded as the name  of a gold coin (probably bearing signs in straight lines);<BR>used in Vijayanagara inscriptions;<BR>probably, revenue income in cash.

rekhaadaNDa|रेखादण्ड
rekhā-daṇḍa  (EI 14), name of a linear measure.

reSha|रेष
reṣa  (IE 8-8), meaning uncertain.

rintakaavaDDi|रिन्तकावड्डि
