rūpaka  (IE 8-8;<BR>EI 30;<BR>CII 4), name of a coin of silver;<BR>cf. kṛṣṇarāja-rūpaka (EI 25;<BR>CII 4), a silver coin issued by the Kalacuri king Kṛṣṇarāja;<BR>silver coin (1/16) of the value of a gold dīnāra in the Gupta age (JNSI, Vol. II, p. 5);<BR>same as dramma.

