ShaNDagula|षण्डगुल
ṣaṇḍa-gula  (LP), same as Gujarātī khāṁḍ-gol, i. e. sugar and molasses.

sandhi|सन्धि
sandhi  (EI 4;<BR>SITI), literally, ‘twilight’;<BR>but actually, ‘service in the temple in the morning and evening’;<BR>daily worship in temples;<BR>special worship offered in the names of persons who arrange for it by creating endowments, etc.

sandhipaata|सन्धिपात
