vaidarveyaka|वैदर्वेयक
vaidarveyaka,  cf. vedaveyaka (IA 18;<BR>CII 1), an eel.

vaidharaNa|वैधरण
vaidharaṇa  (HRS), a compensation fee levied upon the sale of liquors, royal merchandise, mining products and imported salt, as suggested by the Arthaśāstra.

vaidila|वैदिल
vaidila  (CII 3), a word of uncertain import.

vaidya|वैद्य
Vaidya  (EI 9, 30;<BR>BL), a physician;<BR>member of the physician community.

vaidyabhaaga|वैद्यभाग
