vaijaka|वैजक
Vaijaka  (EI 26), official designation;<BR>probably Vaidyaka.

vaijayika|वैजयिक
vaijayika,  carrying victory;<BR>cf. Ep. Ind., XXXII, p. 88. See vijaya-vaijayika.

vaijayikadharmasthaana|वैजयिकधर्मस्थान
