vaamanamudraa|वामनमुद्रा
vāmana-mudrā  (SITI), figures of śaṅkha and cakra marked on the boundary stones set up to demarcate the lands of a Viṣṇu temple. Cf. Vāmana-kkal, boundary stone of land granted for religious purposes.

vaaMphaya|वांफय
