vaMshya|वंश्य
vaṁśya,  same as dhvaṁśī (q. v.).

vana|वन
vana,  a source of income. See Ghoshal, H. Rev. Syst., pp. 109-10. Cf. nāga-vana (IE 8-4), an elephant-forest.

vanachara|वनचर
