vaNijjaaraka|वणिज्जारक
Vaṇijjāraka  (BL), probably, merchants or traders of caravans;<BR>cf. Vaṇajāraka.

vaNik|वणिक्
Vaṇik  (IE 8-3;<BR>BL), merchant or a member of the merchantile community.

