vel8l8i  (EI 15), name of a coin.

venaa|वेना
venā  (EI 31), a kind of grass.

veNii|वेणी
veṇī  (IA 17), a stream or river.

venkaTavilaasamaNTapa|वेङ्कटविलासमण्टप
veṅkaṭa-vilāsa-maṇṭapa  (ASLV), hall in which the royal council met at Vijayanagara.

veNThe|वेण्ठे
vē2ṇṭhē2  (EI 16;<BR>ASLV), same as viṣaya, nirvṛtti, koṭṭam, etc.;<BR>an administrative division;<BR>also called vē2ṇṭhē2ya, vaṇtya, vē2ṭha, vē2ṭa.

veNTheya|वेण्ठेय
vē2ṇṭhē2ya  (EI 16), a sub-division or district;<BR>same as vē2ṇṭhē2.

vergaDe|वेर्गडे
Vē2rgaḍē2  (IE 8-3), Kannaḍa;<BR>same as Vē2ggaḍē2, Pē2rgaḍē2, Hē2ggaḍē2, etc.;<BR>also Sanskrit Adhyakṣa, Adhikārin (a superintendent or governor).

